s beside the table and continues holding up the Halo Top pint while facing the angel. The room’s background includes cloud-painted window panels, a white counter, a white toaster-like appliance, a golden decorative object, and a white harp near the wall. The devil-like man’s expressions shift from surprise to irritation and disbelief as he gestures with the pint. The angel remains seated, calm and delighted, looking up at him with a smile as though enjoying the product or the exchange.\n\nThe confrontation becomes more physical. The horned man moves behind the angel’s chair, looming close over his shoulder while still holding the pint. To the left, the white harp suddenly breaks apart or vanishes into a spray of sparkling dust, leaving glitter-like particles in the air. The angel recoils and turns his head sharply, eyes wide and mouth open, startled by what is happening behind him. The devil-like man briefly crouches or ducks near the back wall under the arch, partly hidden behind the angel and the table.\n\nThe angel sits at the round table surrounded by multiple Halo Top containers and small sample cups, while the horned man emerges from behind him and reaches across the tabletop. He gathers up the ice cream pints, taking them from the angel’s space. The angel stays seated, twisting around to watch, his wings spread behind him and his face still surprised. The horned man then heads back toward the open door, clutching a Halo Top pint against his chest. He turns to glance back over his shoulder, framed by the lavender room, cloud murals, white decorative trees, pink chairs, and the open doorway leading back into the cloudy sky.",
